# Inventory: Home (Ubuntu)

##########
#  Each machine should be named in at least one of the role groups below.
#  Every machine should declare a "desktop_type" variable to indicate
#  which X desktop environment should be used.  Options are:
#      kde (the default)
#      mate
##########

